title: Deer Hunter 2004 (full ISO + patch)
description:
All-new graphics engine provides spectacular outdoor locales and realistic animal animations

6 hunting sites covering approximately 25 square miles in diverse locales

3 different species of deer: Whitetail, Blacktail, and Mule Deer

New hunting skills including animal calling and horsemanship

Multiplayer action for up to 16 players via a LAN or the Internet
